      <event start="T311" end="T1090-254">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1090-254" end="T1091-058">Pa ti povem, da je prav lušno, </event>
      <event start="T1091-058" end="T1093-36">tak sproščeno. </event>
      <event start="T1093-36" end="T313">Eee </event>
      <event start="T313" end="T1096-992">zvečer kartamo al pa kaj takiga. </event>
      <event start="T1096-992" end="T314">Pa ... pa tam, </event>
      <event start="T314" end="T1100-934">pa muziko maš kako pa to. </event>
      <event start="T1100-934" end="T315">Mislim, </event>
      <event start="T315" end="T316">ck dolgo ne smejš met muzike, </event>
      <event start="T316" end="T317">ne, </event>
      <event start="T317" end="T1108-919">moreš eee ugasnt, da nena eee drugih motiš, </event>
      <event start="T1108-919" end="T318">ne, </event>
      <event start="T318" end="T1111-132">ampak super je. </event>
      <event start="T1112-254" end="T320">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T320" end="T1113-462">tak da. </event>
      <event start="T1122-894" end="T322">Aha. </event>
      <event start="T322" end="T323">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T323" end="T1127-175">Pa tam pol mata polpenzion? </event>
      <event start="T1127-175" end="T1129-03">Al mata ol inkluziv? </event>
      <event start="T1132-074" end="T1132-76">Aha. </event>
      <event start="T1132-76" end="T1133-983">Ja, ka pa, </event>
      <event start="T1133-983" end="T1136-56">ka pa te opoldne pol? </event>
      <event start="T1140-685" end="T327">Aja, </event>
      <event start="T327" end="T328">pa vija rada dugo spita, </event>
      <event start="T328" end="T1142-743">ne? </event>
      <event start="T1142-743" end="T1144-162">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1144-162" end="T1144-59">Kaj? </event>
      <event start="T1146-789" end="T1147-384">A ne? </event>
      <event start="T1149-595" end="T330">Pa daj mir. </event>
      <event start="T330" end="T331">To bi ga jaz že malo ukrotila. </event>
      <event start="T331" end="T333">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T333" end="T332">on more te budit, </event>
      <event start="T332" end="T334">ne, </event>
      <event start="T334" end="T335">ko si na dopustu, </event>
      <event start="T335" end="T1156-288">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1159-78" end="T1160-295">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1166-28" end="T1166-807">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1176-275" end="T1176-764">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1178-203" end="T342">Ah, seve(), </event>
      <event start="T342" end="T1180-348">seveda. </event>
      <event start="T1180-348" end="T343">Seveda. </event>
      <event start="T343" end="T1182-588">Kaj pa plavata tudi kaj? </event>
      <event start="T1184-4" end="T344">Ne? </event>
      <event start="T344" end="T345">Zaka pa te ne? </event>
      <event start="T345" end="T346">Sej lani je že blo toplo. </event>
      <event start="T346" end="T1187-949">Ni blo? </event>
      <event start="T1189-514" end="T347">A, </event>
      <event start="T347" end="T348">nena še vre voda? [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T348" end="T1195-451">More, more bit topla [smeh] voda, da greš ti? </event>
      <event start="T1195-451" end="T349">Eee veš kaj, </event>
      <event start="T349" end="T350">eee jaz pa, ko vidim to plavo morje, </event>
